<Link id="l00114" /><CodeLine lineNumber="114"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Implementation of format&#95;provider&lt;T&gt; for duration types.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00115" /><CodeLine lineNumber="115"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00116" /><CodeLine lineNumber="116"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// The options string of a duration type has the grammar:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00117" /><CodeLine lineNumber="117"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00118" /><CodeLine lineNumber="118"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   duration&#95;options  ::= &#91;unit&#93;&#91;show&#95;unit &#91;number&#95;options&#93;&#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00119" /><CodeLine lineNumber="119"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   unit              ::= &#96;h&#96;|&#96;m&#96;|&#96;s&#96;|&#96;ms|&#96;us&#96;|&#96;ns&#96;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00120" /><CodeLine lineNumber="120"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   show&#95;unit         ::= &#96;+&#96; | &#96;-&#96;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00121" /><CodeLine lineNumber="121"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   number&#95;options    ::= options string for a integral or floating point type</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00122" /><CodeLine lineNumber="122"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00123" /><CodeLine lineNumber="123"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   Examples</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00124" /><CodeLine lineNumber="124"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   =================================</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00125" /><CodeLine lineNumber="125"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   |  options  | Input | Output    |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00126" /><CodeLine lineNumber="126"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   =================================</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00127" /><CodeLine lineNumber="127"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   | &quot;&quot;        | 1s    | 1 s       |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00128" /><CodeLine lineNumber="128"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   | &quot;ms&quot;      | 1s    | 1000 ms   |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00129" /><CodeLine lineNumber="129"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   | &quot;ms-&quot;     | 1s    | 1000      |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00130" /><CodeLine lineNumber="130"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   | &quot;ms-n&quot;    | 1s    | 1,000     |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00131" /><CodeLine lineNumber="131"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   | &quot;&quot;        | 1.0s  | 1 s    |</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00132" /><CodeLine lineNumber="132"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///   =================================</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00133" /><CodeLine lineNumber="133"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00134" /><CodeLine lineNumber="134"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  If the unit of the duration type is not one of the units specified above,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00135" /><CodeLine lineNumber="135"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  it is still possible to format it, provided you explicitly request a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00136" /><CodeLine lineNumber="136"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  display unit or you request that the unit is not displayed.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00137" /><CodeLine lineNumber="137"></CodeLine>
